    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 6
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_51_02-ngs001.m4a",
      "text": "あ……千紗ちゃん、気合い入ってるな～\nすっかり不安もなくなったみたい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah… Chisa-chan is really fired up~.\nShe seems to have completely lost her anxiety",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 10.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_51_02-chs002.m4a",
      "text": "お姉ちゃん、今のどうだった？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Onee-chan‚ how was that?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 12.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 15.7333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_51_02-chs003.m4a",
      "text": "「うん、なかなか良かったわ\nでも、最後の方、少しだけ軸がブレていたわね」",
      "translations": {
        "en": "“Yeah‚ it was pretty good.\nBut you lost your balance a little at the end.”",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 18.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_51_02-chs004.m4a",
      "text": "……あっ！　そうなんだ\n自分だと全然気付かなかったよ～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Ah! I see.\nI didn’t notice it at all~.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 25.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 28.6666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_51_02-ngs002.m4a",
      "text": "あれ……誰と話してるんだろう……\n千紗ちゃんしかいない、よね……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huh… I wonder who she’s talking to…\nChisa-chan is the only one here‚ right…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 32.9666666667,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_door-open-02.m4a",
          "delay": 4866.6666665999965,
          "startTime": 37.8333333333
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 5000,
          "startTime": 37.9666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_lesson-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "lesson-01-000-noon",
      "startTime": 37.5833333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_51_02-chs005.m4a",
      "text": "あ、渚ちゃん\n渚ちゃんも自主練？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ Nagisa-chan.\nAre you doing self-practice too?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 40.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_51_02-ngs003.m4a",
      "text": "ううん、ちょっと通り掛かったから\nえっと、誰かと話してたみたいだけど……電話してた？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No‚ I was just passing by‚\nand… it looked like you were talking to someone… Were you on the phone?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 46.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_51_02-chs006.m4a",
      "text": "してないよ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No‚ I wasn’t.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 52.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_51_02-ngs004.m4a",
      "text": "え……じゃあ、だ、誰と話してたの……？\nもしかして……幽霊……とか……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eh… T-then‚ who… who were you talking to…?\nCould it be… a ghost… or something…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 58.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_51_02-chs007.m4a",
      "text": "ふふ、違うよ～。幽霊さんと話せたら楽しそうだけど\nそういうのじゃないから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Fufu‚ no~. It would be fun if I could talk to ghosts‚\nbut it’s not like that.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 67.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_51_02-ngs005.m4a",
      "text": "そうなんだ、よ、良かった～……レッスン室に\n幽霊が出るとか言われたら、どうしようかと――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see‚ t-that’s a relief~… If you said there was a ghost\nin the lesson room‚ I wouldn’t know what to do――",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 75.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_51_02-chs008.m4a",
      "text": "今はね、私の中のお姉ちゃん――\n『イマジナリーSISTER』と話してたの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Right now‚ I’m talking to the Saki-chan inside me――\nmy “Imaginary Sister.”",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 82.7666641235,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_51_02-ngs006.m4a",
      "text": "って、全然良くなかった！？\nどうしよう、千紗ちゃんが不思議なこと言ってる……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s not okay at all!?\nWhat should I do? Chisa-chan’s saying weird things…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 88.0999974568,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_51_02-chs009.m4a",
      "text": "だ、大丈夫だよ～\nこれはね、さくらちゃんから教えてもらったの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I-it’s okay~.\nSakura-chan taught me this.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 94.6333307902,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_51_02-chs010.m4a",
      "text": "みんなのモノマネをすれば、一人じゃないって思えて\nソロでライブをする時も心強いよ、って！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "She said if I impersonate everyone‚ I’ll feel like I’m not alone‚\nand it’ll give me confidence when I do a solo live show!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 102.6999974568,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_51_02-chs011.m4a",
      "text": "やってみたら、私の中にお姉ちゃんが\n降りてきた感じがして、すっごく安心出来たの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "When I tried it‚ it felt like Saki-chan descended into me‚\nand I felt really reassured.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 109.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_51_02-chs012.m4a",
      "text": "今ではモノマネを超えた存在……イマジナリー\nSISTERとして、アドバイスまでくれるんだ～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Now she’s more than just an impersonation… She’s my Imaginary\nSister‚ and she even gives me advice~.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 117.5333307902,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_51_02-chs013.m4a",
      "text": "今も、「もっと指先まで意識して」とか\n「アイソレーション、いい感じね」とか言ってくれて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Even now‚ she’s telling me things like‚ “Be more aware of\nyour fingertips‚” and “Your isolation is looking good.”",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 126.2666641235,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_51_02-ngs007.m4a",
      "text": "千紗ちゃん……\n何か嫌なことがあったなら、いつでも相談に乗るよ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Chisa-chan…\nIf something’s bothering you‚ you can always talk to me.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 132.1333307902,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_51_02-chs014.m4a",
      "text": "ふぇ～！？　だ、大丈夫だってば～\n私には、イマジナリーSISTERがついてるから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huh!? I-I’m fine.\nI have my Imaginary Sister.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 140.3333307902,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_51_02-chs015.m4a",
      "text": "「千紗、もしストレスが溜まってるなら、お姉ちゃんと\nお出掛けしましょうか。スタンプラリーなんてどう？」",
      "translations": {
        "en": "“Chisa‚ if you’re stressed‚ why don’t we go out\nwith me? How about a stamp rally?”",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 148.066670227,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_51_02-chs016.m4a",
      "text": "ありがとう。でも、お姉ちゃんも忙しいと思うし\n一緒にご飯を食べるだけでも大丈夫だよ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thank you. But I think Saki-chan’s busy‚\nso it’s okay if we just eat dinner together.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 156.5333368937,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_51_02-ngs008.m4a",
      "text": "想像上の沙季ちゃんに気を遣ってる……！？\nと、とりあえず時間もあるし、私で良ければ練習見るよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "She’s worried about her imaginary Saki-chan…!?\nW-well‚ we have time‚ so I’ll watch your practice if you want.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 164.0000035603,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 9466.669209900005,
          "startTime": 173.4666727702
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_door-open-02.m4a",
          "delay": 9233.335876500007,
          "startTime": 173.2333394368
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 170.3166763305
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 170.3166763305
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_51_02-ngs009.m4a",
      "text": "それじゃあ、私は行くね\nふぅ……イマジナリーSISTERかぁ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ I’m going to go.\nSigh… An Imaginary Sister‚ huh…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 175.0000061035,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 179.3333429972
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_51_02-ngs010.m4a",
